# Force LF for bash/shell scripts (required for Linux/macOS CI runners)
scripts/claudectl        text eol=lf
tests/helpers/fake-claude text eol=lf
tests/test_claudectl.sh  text eol=lf
setup.sh                 text eol=lf

# CRLF for Windows-native files
*.cmd                    text eol=crlf
*.ps1                    text eol=crlf

# LF for everything else
*.yml                    text eol=lf
*.md                     text eol=lf
*.json                   text eol=lf
*.svg                    text eol=lf
